      <title>Fixing Open Browser on Burpsuite</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/napkins/fixing-open-browser-on-burpsuite/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Dec 2025 18:37:54 -0500</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/napkins/fixing-open-browser-on-burpsuite/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Sharing a helpful fix for the Ubuntu 24.04 error with BurpSuite from Web-Pentester Anthony Hanel&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://anthonyhanel.me/posts/Fixing-Burp-Suite&#39;s-Default-Browser-Ubuntu-24.04/&#34;&gt;https://anthonyhanel.me/posts/Fixing-Burp-Suite&#39;s-Default-Browser-Ubuntu-24.04/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
